  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/356d7af0595ad0edd15e600f6cf904ca.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><strong>Destroy as many tentacles as you can, gather enough flesh to strengthen your Ooze, and annihilate the mighty Ancient Gods.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/9e960dbd4d1eb9b972653f9e6f3d1686.apng?t=1731250188\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/9e960dbd4d1eb9b972653f9e6f3d1686.poster.avif?t=1731250188\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=53 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/7efe106c8da7e8d25dce238b2330e3f3.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prepare your game and aim for the highest score.</h2>Accumulate perseverance points by defeating the Ancient God! Spend them at the beginning of the game to increase the difficulty and achieve a better score. <br>Will you rise to the top of the leaderboard?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/5bcef486253813d082acd912b13b7c66.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control your sanity!</h2>The world is hostile, and madness looms over you. Your sanity is impacted by the mere presence of your enemies, their counterattacks, and the passage of time. It's up to you to regain your balance by eliminating the creeping threat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/85a15c407c3580b381e1467756e357f1.poster.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/85a15c407c3580b381e1467756e357f1.webm?t=1731250188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/85a15c407c3580b381e1467756e357f1.mp4?t=1731250188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be cautious of your life!</h2>Movement comes at a cost; study the terrain carefully and move wisely. Some prefer to charge headfirst and lay the foundations for their successors...<br>The choice is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/48db8bfad62cbac0041b2f7ec6a4114a.poster.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/48db8bfad62cbac0041b2f7ec6a4114a.webm?t=1731250188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/48db8bfad62cbac0041b2f7ec6a4114a.mp4?t=1731250188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sacrifice yourself at the right moment!</h2>Your Ooze is weak. Sacrifice it before its death to strengthen the power of the next one. But beware, you have only a limited number!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/6e96a6cc027aeb3c2f034e3b18717b6a.poster.avif?t=1731250188\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/6e96a6cc027aeb3c2f034e3b18717b6a.webm?t=1731250188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/9e960dbd4d1eb9b972653f9e6f3d1686.apng?t=1731250188\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/9e960dbd4d1eb9b972653f9e6f3d1686.poster.avif?t=1731250188\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=53 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/5f6e8369cfb0bf937da963c39c40b1f5.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>- Quick matches!</strong> Between 3 and 5 minutes maximum to annihilate the Ancient God.<br><strong>- Random generation:</strong> The terrain will never be the same, nor the placement of your enemies.<br><strong>- Configurable difficulty:</strong> Use your experience to increase the difficulty whenever you want.<br><strong>- Scoring:</strong> The higher the difficulty, the more points you will earn!<br><strong>- Risk and Reward:</strong> Manage your movements, your life, and your mental health. Find the right balance to survive!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/9e960dbd4d1eb9b972653f9e6f3d1686.apng?t=1731250188\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/9e960dbd4d1eb9b972653f9e6f3d1686.poster.avif?t=1731250188\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=53 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/c3f352d849f98b7e23a3bcdae978b050.avif?t=1731250188\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br>This game was conceived and designed solely by me, BloodyHand, in a completely self-taught manner and during my free time. Core, design, all created with passion!<br><br>I hope you enjoy it.",
